9 An Act relating to justifiable homicide; amending 21
O.S. 2021, Section 732, which relates to justifiable
10 homicide by officer; authorizing appeal of certain
ruling to Court of Criminal Appeals; requiring
11 priority be given to certain appeals; providing for
waiver of certain right; and providing an effective
12 date.
13
14
15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 21 O.S. 2021, Section 732, is
17 amended to read as follows:
18 Section 732. A. A peace officer, correctional officer, or any
19 person acting by his command in his aid and assistance, is justified
20 in using deadly force when:
21 1. The officer is acting in obedience to and in accordance with
22 any judgment of a competent court in executing a penalty of death;
23 or
